Version 4.0 brings the biggest update to WikiTest so far:

- New darker theme
- New icon and general design updates
- Touch To Peek on calculator
- Redesigned, single peek screen
- Crib on peek screen
- Session History option on peek screen
- New Quick Actions to quickly redirect and view history
- Logout prompt to prevent accidental logouts

Pro Tools:
- Image Peek on Apple Watch
- New (beta) article text mode
- Live Peek history
- Automatic Pairing enhanced and now out of beta for all Pro Tools users

- And a lot more bug fixes, tweaks and enhancements!
